      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>careful support and friends... i dont know. it just feels so hollow. like the part of me that actually lived is just gone. everyone says it gets better but every day just feels like a repeat of the same empty routine. it's like i'm just performing being alive but there's no point to it anymore. what's the point of even trying to \"navigate\" through a life that's already been broken?",
